f gravitational structure formation simulations,\nas observed in galaxy clusters. Finally, we find a strong heavy metal abundance\ngradient in the ISM similar to those observed in massive galaxy groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Oct 2010 20:04:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Jan 2011 01:09:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
