lows for mixed finite element methods to be\napplied to semilinear problems on surfaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Oct 2010 05:50:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2011 19:17:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-01"}
